    "description": "<strong>曾经的我们以为......在太阳灭亡之前，人类还有几十亿年的时间。<br>我们，是错的。</strong><br>掌舵吧，在这重重危机中驶往未知的世代飞船上，去搜寻人类的下一个家园！由致<br>力开发太空创新游戏《家园3》 和《迷走深空:碎舰师》的Blackbird Interactive工作室<br>操刀，《万线生机》是一款融合肉鸽卡牌与战棋策略的科幻主题游戏。你将在茫茫星<br>海中谱绘出你的航线、保卫你的人民，来存续人类文明的火种。而牺牲无法避免，<br>人类的救赎之路将由众多星舰的残骸所铺成.......<br>.....有多少牺牲 ，将取决于你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重任在肩</h2>肩负起拯救人类的重任，在这变幻莫测、危机四伏的浩瀚星河中，舰长，你需要确保<br>你的舰船和船上的每一个生命的生存。每一片星空都会向你展现不同的姿态，层层<br>的险境需要你以不断演化的领导与抉择来克服。残酷的决定、痛苦的失误......都将<br>使你成长，助你探索更遥远的深空。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/0c1fbe08ade767259091ab44a35b400a.poster.avif?t=1752184111\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/0c1fbe08ade767259091ab44a35b400a.webm?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/0c1fbe08ade767259091ab44a35b400a.mp4?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运筹帷幄</h2>星际旅行往往九死一生。舰长，能否从充满敌意的外星生命和太空险象中保卫你的<br>星舰，将取决于你。熟悉你的筹码，在每一次航程中探索强力的卡组、道具和装备。 在战术沙盘上步步为营 ，为你的船员争取每一线可贵的生机和斗争的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/28723f1984692a56ed68a605a83d0753.poster.avif?t=1752184111\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/28723f1984692a56ed68a605a83d0753.webm?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/28723f1984692a56ed68a605a83d0753.mp4?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >上下一心</h2>在每一段航程中，都会有一队新的舰员由你任用。细心观察他们的特质与需求，量<br>体裁衣，才能发挥出他们每个人最大的力量——反之，漠视他们则会招致恶果。尽<br>忠职守的团队是每一位舰长的利刃——你，可以与他们上下一心吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/429b2ec0302ad46a59b3f839bef09eef.poster.avif?t=1752184111\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/429b2ec0302ad46a59b3f839bef09eef.webm?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/429b2ec0302ad46a59b3f839bef09eef.mp4?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一同寻找新的家园</h2>你可以在单人冒险中独自启航，或是在多人模式中与友同行。双方各自掌舵，在每<br>一回合中同时操作——将带给你新世代的策略体验。和好友一同展开致命的协同打<br>击、解锁多人模式下的特殊卡牌、激情商议最佳战略！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/76e7cdd5a50d9e537b45235f48059144.poster.avif?t=1752184111\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/76e7cdd5a50d9e537b45235f48059144.webm?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/76e7cdd5a50d9e537b45235f48059144.mp4?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一段不断演化的旅程</h2><br>新的篇章：向宇宙更深处探察、遭遇新的危机、并且寻找最终问题的答案: 我们，真<br>的是宇宙中独行的生命吗?<br>新的阵营：每一个新阵营都有独特的星舰战技和崭新卡组，为你的战略增添新的可<br>能性、解锁新玩法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/da0738589c638914820ee83ce4d840fc.poster.avif?t=1752184111\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058960/extras/da0738589c638914820ee83ce4d840fc.webm?t=1752184111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp